KUDUTSHULWE isisebenzi esineminyaka engu-37 ubudala, esitolo iSpar, eWaterloo, ngaseVerulam, ngesikhathi kuhlasela oshayasibhamu ngoLwesine ebusuku. Kuthiwa abasolwa abebehlome beyizingovolo bagasele eSpar, Tops naseKFC kanyekanye bezobamba inkunzi. Bagebenge lezi zitolo imali, kwabuye kwebiwa notshwala. Okhulumela inkampani yonogada esebenzela kule ndawo, iRusa, uthe abathengi basabalale okwamanzi echitheka ngesikhathi kudutshulwa umphathi waseSpar. “Abanye abathengi kuthiwa bacashe esiqandisini kanti abanye baphume ngesamagundane ngomnyango wangemuva,” kuqhubeka abeRusa. Abazibonele bathi abasolwa bebehamba ngezimoto ezintathu, iVW Polo anezinombolo ezithi iCAA, iToyota Quatum emhlophe neHyundai empunga.